Given an array containing three ints, return the sum of all the elements.
public int sum3(int[] nums)
{

}

Code:
public int sum3(int[] nums) {
    int sum = 0;
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
        sum += nums[i];
    }
    return sum;
}

